Class OutputTrack

  • java.lang.Object
    • Audio.OutputTrack

  • public class OutputTrack
extends java.lang.Object
    Output Track inherits attributes from Track such as set up of Data Line and playback. Output class is used for playback of multiple Tracks(super).
